name: American Airlines First Class, Boeing 737-800, ORD-LAX
description:
In this video, I take a long cross-country flight between Chicago O'Hare and Los Angeles on AA's workhorse, the 737-800. The video includes a few shots at O'Hare, all phases of the flight and onboard service.

Also included - a lovely rainbow while descending into LAX!
